{"tid":1923303,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"1月19「天下制裁」集會被捕7男　3人遭控參與暴動","createTime":"2020-03-13T03:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T12:42:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c0dea365af9a38b0627f114530345c4ccf7b795f","tid":1923303,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"反修例風波延續大半年，今年1月19日舉行的「天下制裁」遮打花園集會終演變成警民衝突，其中有警民關係組便衣警員與主辦方交涉期間被人包圍毆打。警方經調查後於本周三(11日)展開行動，在多區拘捕7名男子，年齡介乎13至34歲，懷疑與案有關。<br />\n<br />\n經深入調查，其中3名年齡介乎19至34歲被捕男子被控「參與暴動」及「有意圖而傷人」，案件將於4月14日在東區裁判法院提堂。另4名介乎13至20歲男子則獲准保釋候查，須於4月中旬向警方報到。"},{"pid":"dff32da64f8b32b2ba57e0926074ae70a53b39a3","tid":1923303,"uid":167506,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:58:25.000Z","msg":"傷人真係無得走"},{"pid":"995cf17f113f65b8866218c286e816e4eff2ffa9","tid":1923303,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8425b0fb2df08c24145c6b87836a94230a6794c","tid":1923303,"uid":352734,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:00:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"838fd28f9b10959f0ee53b7baaa0fcb826602b60","tid":1923303,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e5adf5e208a5282444236031b1723b913a413e","tid":1923303,"uid":185854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyT